en-US.title: East Sydney Doctors
en-US.description: Caring for the community since 1984, East Sydney Doctors provides a full range of healthcare services including sexual health, mental health, preventative health and medicinal cannabis treatment. With a strong focus on education and medical research, the clinic tailors its services to cater to everyone including the transmasculine, non-binary and transfeminine communities. New patients are warmly welcomed to enjoy the relaxed, community based atmosphere of the clinic.
